[extension_name]
Simple TTS

[extension_info]
Created by JzTurrini with the purpose to read the text of the moders out loud. 
Ideal to be used on Microsoft Edge because of neural voices alternatives, but you can use on any browser. 
IMPORTANT: The number of voices is limited in most of them, except on Edge.

[extension_version]
2.2.0

[insert_external]
